subject: Fix TC-1572: Fail to start elf ui launched from dbus.
commitMessage:
Fix TC-1572: Fail to start elf ui launched from dbus.

Enviroment required by EFL framework was missing for process
launched by dbus, so this fix launch the signonui-efl from bash
so that proper environment is set.

Change-Id: If848b4f5743df394388396c2256ccd975779a23c
Signed-off-by: Amarnath Valluri <amarnath.valluri@linux.intel.com>
